title: Renovated Studio in Mission Dolores with Large Closet Space
posting_body: ['240 Dolores Street, San Francisco, CA 94103', 'Apartment 3D Tour (copy and paste): <URL>', "Live between Market Street and Dolores Park, where you'll be near everything you need.", "Stroll over to Maxfield's House of Caffeine to grab a sandwich and smoothie before enjoying a few hours lounging in the sun at Dolores Park.", 'Grab your groceries at Whole Foods or Safeway, both only two blocks from your new home.', 'Getting hungry?', 'There are TONS of bars and restaurants all within a quick 10-minute walk!', 'Nestled between the Mission and Castro Districts, this apartment is near it all!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'for more information!', 'We are currently offering virtual tours and self-guided tours.', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', '-Renovated Unit', '-Hardwood Floors Throughout', '-Kitchenette w/Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Faux Wood Blinds', '-Large Closet Space', 'PROPERTY AMENITIES', '-Rent Controlled Building,', '-Water, Sewer, and Trash Utilities Included in Rent', '-Heated Swimming Pool', '-Controlled Access', '-Laundry Facilities on Site', '-Amazon Hub Package Lockers', '-Parking Available for Additional Fee (Gated or Carport)', "-Located in San Francisco's Castro Neighborhood", 'NEIGHBORHOOD', '-Whole Foods & Safeway (0.2 miles)', '-Muni Metro Station (0.3 miles)', '-16th', 'St BART Station (0.4 miles)', '-Dolores Park (0.3 miles)', '-Shops & Cafes on Market Street (0.3 miles)', '-Restaurants & Bites on Valencia Street', '***Photos are of a similar apartment**', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.']
